Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.69,0:00:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A racing second hand,\Na shooting comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan's logic works wonders on\Nhearts exhausted by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's hints are crabs and a whale!\NUnexpected things look like them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid but\Nhas the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.88,0:00:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:57.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Crabs and Whale Kidnapping Case
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Crabs and Whale Kidnapping Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tastes great! Can't have\Nsummer without beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! You shouldn't just drink!\NYou need to eat a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. Don't be so naggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was all excited when he said\Nit was a fancy hotel dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's nothing but light snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who takes kids\Nto beer gardens to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:42.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dentist - Endo Keigo (33)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man's at a beer garden\Nbut hasn't even had a sip...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you drunk already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bathrooms aren't that way!\NReally, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Endo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Yes. I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the deal off?! I got the\Nmoney and didn't tell the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Let me hear Keita again! Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did this man--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man! Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it out loud,\Nbut I think there was a kidnapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you said, there's a good\Nchance they're holding him for ransom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It sounds like he\Nhasn't contacted the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Driver. Try not to lose\Nthe taxi in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:49.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Endo Dental Clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:07.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Closed for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dentist, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to talk with him first...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't know where\Nthe kidnapper is looking from,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it could be\Na neighbor behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a good idea!\NI'll be a patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, start.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My tooth hurts! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! Dad's going to\Ntalk to the dentist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't hold on! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to bother you\Non your day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My kid's tooth hurts and\Nhe won't shut up about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you look at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. Please come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come into\Nthe examination room...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon my late introduction.\NI am Detective Mori Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori Kogoro? That famous detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So Conan-{\i1}kun {\i0}heard\Nmy phone conversation--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endo-{\i1}san{\i0}. Could you tell me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the kid's right,\Nthen I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. This may be\Nsome sort of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you said,\Nmy son was kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Keita.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I let him play by himself in\Nthe front yard this afternoon, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita! Let's go to the park!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Took the kid. Call the police\Nand he's dead. Wait for a call."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's written on ordinary copy paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what did the kidnapper tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a young man's\Nvoice on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to put 30 million\Nyen in used bills in a briefcase
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and to be at Starlight\NHotel's beer garden at 6:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a little after 6:00, he called\Nme and cancelled the exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he explain why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. All he said was that he would\Ncall again tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the kidnapper was suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably never intended\Nto get the money tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He likely watched Endo-{\i1}san {\i0}from\Nsomewhere in the beer garden
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to make sure he hadn't\Ncontacted the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you got the first call,\Ndid you hear Keita-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I asked the kidnapper\Nto put him on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did Keita-{\i1}kun{\i0} seem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sounded unexpectedly cheerful;\Nhe didn't seem afraid at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is odd. You would expect\Nhim to at least miss his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She died of a disease last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps that's why Keita grew\Nfond of his kindergarten teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the women in the\Nneighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Now I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnapper is likely working\Nwith a woman good with children,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she's taking care of Keita-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning we can't rest easy,\Nbut it's unlikely they'll hurt Keita-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endo-{\i1}san{\i0}. I think you probably\Nshould call the police now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the kidnappers will be\Ncaught if the police intervene!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what guarantee do I have\NKeita will return unharmed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my only hope now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Help bring\NKeita back unharmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well! I was\Nthe one who came to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work together\Nto somehow solve this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't stay here too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave for tonight and\Ntalk on the phone from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need to borrow this photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have nothing to worry about.\NI will return Keita-{\i1}kun {\i0}safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I appreciate your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attached the transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we just wait for\Nthe kidnappers to call!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori Detective Agency...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They called?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did they say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They demanded 20 million more,\Nand gave me two hours to get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear Keita-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I had them put him\Non just like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.22,0:11:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he said something odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita! Is that you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! There's lots\Nof crabs here, Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crabs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! Call the cops and--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A whale! A whale is spouting bubbles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Loudmouthed brat!\NI'll contact you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?! Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Loudmouthed? The kidnapper said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. You get the money ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With any luck, I'll have\NKeita-{\i1}kun {\i0}back within two hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Please do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! You have a clue\Nabout the kidnappers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Keita-{\i1}kun {\i0}is by lots of\Ncrabs and a bubble-spouting whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crabs and a whale?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be dumb! Whales only\Nspout air deep underwater!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a real whale that Keita-{\i1}kun {\i0}saw.\NIt was probably a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A model?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that would be at the aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:28.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Southern Aquarium
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any whale models?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. We do have various kinds\Nof crabs, but no whale models...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Must be a different aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no time! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say... Are you sure the\Ncrabs have to be real?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Keita-{\i1}kun {\i0}said there\Nwere lots of crabs,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:13:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the kidnapper said,\N"What are you talking about?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that mean the\Nkidnapper couldn't see any?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they didn't call\Nfrom the aquarium?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that, Dad! It's a whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:21.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nichiuri TV
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Nichiuri TV's\Nmascot is a whale this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be what Keita-{\i1}kun {\i0}saw?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, then he was\Nwhere that blimp was visible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! The blimp was above\NBeika Park when the kidnappers called!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beika Park?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday's deal was\Nat a hotel on Beika Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back and look\Nfor a place with lots of crabs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita-{\i1}kun {\i0}has to be\Nsomewhere near there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any luck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Our time's up!\NThe kidnappers might've called.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They called two minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They told him to stand at the\Nend of Platform 1 in Karajuku Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karajuku Station?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You keep looking\Nfor the crabs, Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they did lose to the kidnappers,\Nmy transmitter's on the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:26.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Karajuku Station
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think they'll be on a train?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll probably exchange\Nthe money elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw the money here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you care about the kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But Mori-{\i1}san {\i0}got the\Nlicense plate number on film.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll know his identity soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's staying in the same spot.\NTheir hideout should be nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost there!\NJust around that corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! They must've\Nchanged briefcases here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:17:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the old man got the license\Nplate number, so we can still--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was this the kidnapper's?!\NWas that license plate a fake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Now that they have the money,\Nthey might kill Keita-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find where there's lots of crabs\Nand where the whale blimp was visible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't he say the whale\Nwas spouting air bubbles?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That blimp wasn't spouting anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean? Was it not\Nthe blimp he saw?! Or maybe--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't see it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be visible from\Nthat Starlight Hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beika Park. And then that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita-{\i1}kun {\i0}saw the smoke\Nfrom that waste incineration facility...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would look like that only\Nwhere the park and the tower line up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is too low. It needs to\Nbe the same altitude as the blimp
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to make it look like\Nit's spouting air.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could they be in this hotel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tables and chairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could the crabs actually be--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are! The crabs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tables and chairs look\Nlike crabs from above!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it! Keita-{\i1}kun\N{\i0}is in some room in this hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know which room\Nthis boy is staying in?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's in a room one floor down.\NBut he just left with his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I found you!\NKeita-{\i1}kun {\i0}is still unharmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaiba Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Joker! Hiyaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are we really\Ngoing to kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit asking and stop\Nworrying about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are kidnappers!\NStop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Nobody move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move and he's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get over there! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything to kick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bike's right out front!\NRun like hell once we're out the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita! I'm so glad\Nyou're all right! Keita!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy, that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know they were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just dumb luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for the crabs\Nwhen I found Keita-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I shouted that it was a kidnapping,\Nthey rushed to get away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and wound up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.13,0:23:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brought it upon themselves, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Inspector Megure-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun {\i0}explained everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.14,0:23:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you contact us when\Nyou learned it was a kidnapping?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.81,0:23:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't trust me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.11,0:23:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.28,0:23:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the next hour, Inspector Megure\Ngave the old man a good scolding.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.16,0:23:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that that's a bad thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:25.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.37,0:24:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.71,0:24:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a homicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.35,0:24:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be possible\Nto leave from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is there a bloodstain here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.65,0:24:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikuta-{\i1}san {\i0}was standing here in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.83,0:24:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.44,0:24:31.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Pitch Dark Road Murder Case
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.16,0:24:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.44,0:24:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Pitch Dark Road Murder Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.14,0:24:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.71,0:24:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tobacco.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.72,0:24:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode features yet another \Nshocking and impressive trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.88,0:24:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see the crows in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.63,0:24:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
